      "to_metabolic_system": "Mitochondrial dysfunction → reduced fatty acid oxidation → increased lipid accumulation → insulin resistance (BLD_INSULIN_RESISTANCE_001)",
      "to_hormonal_system": "Steroid hormones (cortisol, aldosterone, sex steroids) synthesised in mitochondria — StAR protein transports cholesterol into mitochondria for synthesis"
